<h1>Surfing</h1>

<h2>Beaches</h2>
<p>Dedicated surfing spots are located at:
  <ul>
    <li>Beach 67th to 69st Street (most spacious area)</li>
    <li>Beach 87st to 92nd Street</li>
    <li>Beach 110th to 111th Street</li>
  </ul>
</p>
<p>The A train will take you directly to Beach 67th Street (make sure you're on the Far Rockaway A train). For the other beaches, take the A train to Broad Channel, and switch to the shuttle train.</p>
<p>Technically, you could also take the 2 train to Brooklyn College, then the Q35 bus to Riis Beach, and the Q22 bus down to any of these beaches. It may take you longer depending on where you're coming from. </p>

